#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:239
msgid ""
"For example, line 5 declares an image named \"sylvie smile\", found in the "
"filename \"sylvie_smile.png\", with the tag \"sylvie\"."
msgstr ""
"例えば5行目では、ファイル名「sylvie_smile.png」で見つかる「sylvie smile」とい"
